PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1993-927 of May 6, 1993 which appointed BRIGADIER-GENERAL PIERRE G. BOUTET, C.D., as Judge Advocate General of the Canadian Forces by revoking the words "for a term of four years" and substituting the words "for a term ending November 2, 1997".
